data.description: Come see this Briargate beauty! Built in 1983 This 4 bedroom, 4 bath home is packed with extras. You get 3 large living spaces including one in the basement for use as a game room, home theater, play room, or anything you can dream up. There is a mudroom/workshop between the garage and the lower level entry. You also get a 10x12 detached workshop, with power, storage attic, and a ramp adjacent to the paved third driveway. There are 2 storage sheds on the property. The paved additional parking is ready for your RV. This 8993 sq ft lot features a huge back yard ready for entertaining with a  15x15 wooden deck and 120 SqFt patio with a propane fire pit and lots of lighting! The yard has been 85% xeriscaped with a drip irrigation system for the flower beds, trees, and shrubs. The lawn area in the back has automated irrigation and is very easy to maintain. The lower living room opens to the sun room, which includes furniture and a heater for year round enjoyment. The kitchen features Corian countertops, stainless steel appliances and lots of storage. Featuring waterproof RVP flooring throughout the main floor, in the laundry room and mudroom. The master and basement baths have custom showers with barn doors. The basement bedroom can be used as a 2nd master with an attached bathroom. Come check out his unique Colorado build today!
